{{Flavour|A deep elf learned in the ways of murderous magic. It is capable of casting a wide array of harmful spells.}}

==Useful Info==
'''Deep elf mages''' are flimsy but unpredictable [[list of deep elves|deep elf]] casters, capable of hitting you with a wide variety of spells, though at reassuringly low [[spell power]]. While never harmless, they pale in comparison to some of the deadlier deep elf varieties. They can be found roaming the later floors of [[the Dungeon]] on their own, and often appear in packs with other deep elves in the [[Elven Halls]], [[the Vaults]] and some [[bailey]]s.

