==Tips & Tricks==
Although far from harmless, prioritize taking out the other deep elves before attacking these.

==History==
*Deep elf magi were split into [[deep elf pyromancer]]s and [[deep elf zephyrmancer]]s in [[0.27]].
*Prior to [[0.25]], the Conjuration-focused spell set had [[Iskenderun's Mystic Blast]] instead of [[Force Lance]].
*In [[0.18]], Deep elf mages became stronger and gained new spell sets, including spells previously cast by [[deep elf conjurer]]s and [[deep elf summoner|summoners]]. 
*Prior to [[0.13]], deep elf mages had spell sets identical to a [[wizard (monster)|wizard's]], including such devastating spells as [[Banishment]] and [[Lehudib's Crystal Spear]].

